Introduction

S#aFLA (Korean: 샤플라; ShaFLA) was a four-member girl group under VINE Entertainment. They debuted on October 18, 2018 with their first digital single "S#aFLA NO.1".

They presumably disbanded in late 2019, after the group stopped celebrating members' birthdays on their official accounts and all the members (beside Yujin) were unfollowed by VINE Entertainment.
